data.description: This charming home is the perfect place to settle down and make memories. From the natural color palette to the cozy fireplace, this property offers many desirable features. The primary bathroom features good under sink storage, and the flexible living space includes other rooms for versatile use. The roof is new, and the interior and exterior have both been freshly painted. There has also been partial flooring replacement in some areas. This home is ready for you to move in and make it your own. Don't miss out on this one! This home has been virtually staged to illustrate its potential.
